202
00:18:42,735 --> 00:18:44,396
Vas-y.

203
00:18:57,416 --> 00:18:59,941
Tu es un mauvais garçon,
S- man.

204
00:19:00,119 --> 00:19:01,347
Et Cuch?

205
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,680
